{"type": "article", "id": 34344, "title": "特朗普当选总统，支持他的彼得·蒂尔又成眼光最好的投资人了", "description": "人嘛，说话总是变来变去的。", "date": "2016-11-10T23:08:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1128, "name": "LGBT"}, {"id": 8892, "name": "大选"}, {"id": 66, "name": "Facebook"}, {"id": 3102, "name": "Paypal"}, {"id": 5964, "name": "Founders Fund"}, {"id": 2438, "name": "扎克伯格"}, {"id": 10999, "name": "彼得·蒂尔"}, {"id": 18586, "name": "特朗普"}], "category": 4, "author": 392200, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161110205738h85tRoY3nlx0Urqj.jpg", "contents": "<p cid=\"c366\" mdtype=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"https://encrypted.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjQk8PqmJ7QAhUDfLwKHeD0B10QFggiMAE&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2016%2F07%2F21%2Fpeter-thiel-gives-full-throated-endorsement-of-donald-trump%2F&amp;usg=AFQjCNHaDJV_3PZ9kdX1wIa8VhwdadFnDg&amp;sig2=RBWT-L9NGhrVPPsFN55DYA\" rel=\"nofollow\">因为公开支持特朗普</a>，而且还在他“更衣室事件”发生后<a href=\"https://encrypted.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjTs9L1mJ7QAhXEu7wKHQ4EC1IQFgggMAE&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Ffeatures%2F2016%2F10%2F17%2Freport-tech-billionaire-peter-thiel-to-donate-1-25m-for-trump.html&amp;usg=AFQjCNEyfYFiaeVVanEBd2UG5LWibI0QSw&amp;sig2=Py5-3Nu0eEkfBgJ9L3FJeg&amp;bvm=bv.138169073,d.dGc\" rel=\"nofollow\">捐了 125 万美元</a>助选，著名创业家、风险投资人彼得·蒂尔（Peter Thiel）在大选前一下子从神坛掉落。</p><p cid=\"c464\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">没办法，谁让他选择当硅谷的异类呢。</p><p cid=\"c467\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">基本上整个硅谷乃至科技界都在支持克林顿，<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/10/technology/peter-thiel-bet-donald-trump-wins-big.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">至少明面上是这样</a>。比方说<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"http://www.npr.org/sections/alltechconsidered/2016/10/31/500114584/peter-thiel-stands-out-in-silicon-valley-for-support-of-donald-trump\" rel=\"nofollow\">有 95% 的科技公司员工支持克林顿</a>，硅谷企业和员工给克林顿捐款金额<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/2016-election-day/silicon-valley-donated-60-times-more-clinton-trump-n679156\" rel=\"nofollow\">是特朗普的 60 倍</a>。</p><p cid=\"c469\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">这么一来，彼得·蒂尔给特朗普捐助选资金，使他成为众矢之的。</p><p cid=\"c469\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">事后不少媒体<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://encrypted.google.com/search?rlz=1C1CHZL_zh-CNUS711&amp;{google:acceptedSuggestion}oq=reomve+peter+thiel&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;q=reomve+peter+thiel#newwindow=1&amp;q=remove+peter+thiel\" rel=\"nofollow\">建议 Facebook 把蒂尔踢出董事会</a>，被首席执行官扎克伯格以“<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/oct/19/peter-thiel-support-donald-trump-mark-zuckerberg\" rel=\"nofollow\">公司深切关注多样性</a>”为由挡了回去。而面向 <a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.advocate.com/commentary/2016/10/14/peter-thiel-shows-us-theres-difference-between-gay-sex-and-gay\" rel=\"nofollow\">LGBT 杂志 The Advocate 干脆开除蒂尔 “Gay 籍”</a>。</p><p cid=\"c430\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">不过现在特朗普当选了，蒂尔当初的选择就变成了<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2016/11/09/peter-thiels-big-gamble/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“赌对了”</a> 。如果你在 Twitter 上搜索&nbsp;<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?f=tweets&amp;vertical=news&amp;q=peter%20thiel%20&amp;src=typd\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peter Thiel</a>，出来的结果基本是人们转发<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2016/11/09/peter-thiels-big-gamble/\" rel=\"nofollow\">《彼得·蒂尔的大赌博》</a>、<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/10/technology/peter-thiel-bet-donald-trump-wins-big.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">《彼得·蒂尔对特朗普的赌注得到回报</a>》等文章。</p><p cid=\"c433\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">一下子他又变成了曾经那个最有眼光的投资人：创办了 Paypal 并以 <a href=\"https://encrypted.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=3&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;sqi=2&amp;ved=0ahUKEwilhY3vmZ7QAhUINrwKHQxlAnIQFgglMAI&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Fnews%2Febay-picks-up-paypal-for-1-5-billion%2F&amp;usg=AFQjCNFR8saCr4xkrGXSDin2O3mKd2PRjg&amp;sig2=1SDM1WR6DYNz9e3OIYhnCQ&amp;bvm=bv.138169073,d.dGc\" rel=\"nofollow\">15 亿美元</a>卖给 Ebay 成功套现；投资 50 万美元换回 Facebook 10% 股份，还进入了董事会，现在 Facebook 成为了全球最值钱的五家科技公司之一；后来创办了大数据公司 Palantir 并以 200 亿美元估值成为硅谷估值最高的科技公司之一。 </p><p cid=\"c360\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">除此之外，蒂尔通过其风险投资公司 Founders Fund，<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/5100.html\">投资 SpaceX、Airbnb 等创业公司</a>，它们今天都是各自领域内最好的公司之一。</p><p cid=\"c491\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">这里还有个事情大概也能歪打正着地说明彼得·蒂尔的投资有眼光。</p><p cid=\"c509\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" class=\"\">两年前，Founders Fund 参与了<a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/weed-startup-privateer-raises-75-million-at-425-million-valuation-2014-12\" rel=\"nofollow\">大麻产业初创公司 Privateer 某轮 7500 万美元的融资</a>，当时全美至少有 22 个州允许大麻被用于医疗用途。Privateer 估计大麻在美国有 200 亿美元到 500 亿美元的市场。</p><p cid=\"c520\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">而就在昨天，更支持克林顿的加州<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2016/11/8/13520486/marijuana-legalization-california-election-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">通过法律把娱乐性吸食大麻（Recreational marijuana）在当地合法化了</a>。</p><p cid=\"c526\" mdtype=\"paragraph\">据市场调研机构 Arcview 估计，加州现在合法大麻市场（指药用）大约有 21 亿美元，到 2020 年如果医用和普通成年人都可以吸食，<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/2016/06/30/theres-a-new-gold-rush-in-california-as-investors-prep-for-pot-legalization-vote.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">这个市场将扩大到 64 亿美元。</a></p><p cid=\"c526\" mdtype=\"paragraph\"><br></p><p cid=\"c526\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://encrypted.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjL7d7CnJ7QAhWEUrwKHVPKALcQjB0IBg&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fnews%2F2016%2F09%2Fpeter-thiel-supreme-court&amp;bvm=bv.138169073,d.dGc&amp;psig=AFQjCNGQ1H9L2qNZ1FXEzHuZ8pukUVVtRw&amp;ust=1478868446900633\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vanity Fair</a></p>"}